# WiselyFox Core

- Next.js 15 App Router + TypeScript
- CSS Modules only — no Tailwind
- Feature-based structure under `src/features/`
- Business logic in `src/server/services/` — never import React there
- Validate all server inputs with Zod
- No placeholders; document deferrals in `docs/BACKLOG.md`
- Add tests for every critical feature
